{"tid":888838,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【電競】「電競．BlizzCon」香港爐石代表8強止步　平上屆成績","createTime":"2018-11-04T05:58:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-04T06:52:48.000Z","uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"719d5afc939178514dc4e83e8d381f9d1003c971","tid":888838,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T05:58:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2050336/org/73de3ed405c5939135222d9f89fa2830.jpg/JPbzl2SCjoKOluioW1A-VjBtCfoN9zdeP4FasD-BWrA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2050336%2Forg%2F73de3ed405c5939135222d9f89fa2830.jpg%2FJPbzl2SCjoKOluioW1A-VjBtCfoN9zdeP4FasD-BWrA&h=7944836f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2049964/org/81507b9f67bf87234b3fe733460b1d63.png/A19ttE0hraSsgV8CmCK67hZ0dGhz-oATgK8vUoCvL1I\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2049964%2Forg%2F81507b9f67bf87234b3fe733460b1d63.png%2FA19ttE0hraSsgV8CmCK67hZ0dGhz-oATgK8vUoCvL1I&h=53ff7b40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本年「電競．BlizzCon」相信令不少香港人不惜捱更抵夜追看，但聽到「DIABLO」推出手機版，難免令不少朋友憤而關機「早唞」。<br />\n<br />\n其實，關機之後，爐石戰記香港代表正為香港戰鬥。雖然8強止步，未能突破上年成績，但表現毫不失禮。<br />\n<br />\n港隊今次派出的選手，包括亞運金牌選手KIN，其餘3名選手包括blitzchung、SHY及Losefield，在國際場上都有一定的成績。比賽直播時，賽評都說今年香港隊十分強勁，在第一戰時以局數3：2戰勝西班牙，但在8強第2輪時，負中國2：3。港隊進入敗部決賽遇上新西蘭，爭入4強。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新西蘭在小組賽首名出線，雖然第一戰時局數1:3負中國，但實力不能小看。始終卡牌遊戲，有一定運氣成分使然，而香港代表今戰就是輸給了運氣。<br />\n<br />\n港隊在第一戰，blitzchung用了「魚人法師」牌組，整個過程都十分順利，先勝局數1:0。第2局由KIN上陣，賽評於賽事期間對這位亞運金牌選手，不乏讚美之言。但KIN未能打破牌組克制的問題而敗陣，打成1：1。其後，SHY用上薩滿，讓港隊再領先，但新西蘭在隨後兩局，手氣極佳，連勝兩局，令港隊被後來居上，負2：3，繼去年再次8強止步。而前香港爐石第一選手JEANNO，評論港隊表現亦坦言新西蘭隊手氣好:「我覺得港隊發揮比較好，但對方手氣好，令港隊每場都劣勢對局，真的有點難對付。」"},{"pid":"0d5963fcb4734c1bbdef57a3923179f9d5e45988","tid":888838,"uid":46286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T06:28:38.000Z","msg":"手氣問題 ....."},{"pid":"92a6ab07d3bc7cb0db6cc46eeeba4503432797f2","tid":888838,"uid":86337,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T06:34:42.000Z","msg":"咪又係靠運氣入8強<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3a3d8f78e99f48316a864687fda101dc6e21577","tid":888838,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T06:43:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c4ab0017cc4984716da466b922ecbb984a096c5","tid":888838,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T06:44:35.000Z","msg":"有無人知有無獎金？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf073943e44b19f62bd99bd712378a3f454ac01d","tid":888838,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T06:48:06.000Z","msg":"一輸就賴欠運 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f1b3ca1e806dd28906cdd498ba3b75c04b00e36","tid":888838,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T06:48:26.000Z","msg":"之前連登仲嘈緊爐石唔係運氣Game <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5406aee4e8bf8019fa73cb1ab22ddc13435d26c","tid":888838,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T06:51:24.000Z","msg":"爐氣運氣佔成份太多<br />\n<br />\n皇室 戰爭得8張牌，一開波抽得衰都好易落下風，何況30張牌"},{"pid":"69e30d1c9453c23aa78760aa364ec69c6596587c","tid":888838,"uid":213300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T06:52:48.000Z","msg":"都唔知條友評論乜尻 輸打贏要<br />\n贏就嬴實力<br />\n輸就輸運氣 弱撚智"}]}